        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-1" parent="1" style="text;html=1;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingTop=-4;fontSize=22;fontStyle=1" value="OptionB:&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(35, 47, 62); text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Hybrid NLP + XGBoost Pipeline 를 활용한 NOTAM 영향도 분석&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="30" width="700" x="10" y="-70" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-2" parent="1" style="line;strokeWidth=2;html=1;fontSize=14;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="10" width="1550" x="10" y="-25" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-3" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontStyle=1" value="Phase 1 (Training): 파인튜닝한 BERT/BART 계열의 모델로 NOTAM 텍스트를 이해시킨 후, XGBoost로 지연 확률을 예측하는 2단계 하이브리드 ML 파이프라인" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="310" x="1730" y="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-4" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;fontStyle=1" value="Phase 2 (Inference): Lambda가 NLP 특징 추출과 외부 데이터 조회를 병렬 실행(①)한 뒤, 통합된 feature vector로 XGBoost가 최종 지연 확률 예측(②)" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="50" width="290" x="1730" y="568" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-5" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1" value="&lt;pre class=&quot;jss761&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-testid=&quot;qbiz-components-markdown-codehighlighter-fallback-container&quot;&gt;API Response sample&lt;br&gt;   └─→ JSON 응답&lt;br&gt;   {&lt;br&gt;       &quot;flight_id&quot;: &quot;7C123&quot;,&lt;br&gt;       &quot;delay_probability&quot;: 0.78,&lt;br&gt;       &quot;risk_level&quot;: &quot;High&quot;,&lt;br&gt;       &quot;contributing_factors&quot;: [&lt;br&gt;           &quot;Runway closure (High impact)&quot;,&lt;br&gt;           &quot;Poor weather visibility&quot;,&lt;br&gt;           &quot;High airport congestion&quot;&lt;br&gt;       ],&lt;br&gt;       &quot;recommendation&quot;: &quot;Consider alternative routing&quot;&lt;br&gt;   }&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="230" width="430" x="1730" y="628" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-9" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#FDD835;strokeWidth=1.5;arcSize=6;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="185" width="280" x="20" y="858" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-10" parent="1" style="text;html=1;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;fontColor=#F57F17;" value="&lt;b&gt;Option B 특징&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="20" width="150" x="30" y="868" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="236U1vujBufm9aVvuARd-11" parent="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;spacingLeft=5;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;b&gt;높은 정밀도&lt;/b&gt; — 실측 데이터 기반 수치 예측&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;정량적 예측&lt;/b&gt; — 지연 확률(%)을 직접 산출&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;설명 가능&lt;/b&gt; — Feature Importance로 근거 제시&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;낮은 추론 비용&lt;/b&gt; — Serverless Endpoint 활용&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;확장 가능&lt;/b&gt; — 외부 데이터 결합 용이 (기상, 혼잡도)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#D32F2F&quot;&gt;⚠ 대량 학습 데이터 필요 (수만 건 이상)&lt;br&gt;⚠ 초기 구축 기간 3~6개월&lt;br&gt;⚠ 한국어 요약/브리핑 불가 (별도 LLM 필요)&lt;/font&gt;&#xa;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="155" width="260" x="30" y="873" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
